New stall at this coffee shop.  Good roasted meat stall especially the roast pork and char siew pork ribs.  Very generous serving and every order comes with a nice Szechuan preserved vege soup.
Reasonable taste of Roast Duck & Roast Pork cum Char Siew Rice
Recently relocated from Blk 59, fragrant and tender roast duck. I usually order without the sauce for health reason yet the duck meat is tasty enough with just plain rice.
The roast duck is nice. Price is reasonable too.

News stall just open. The food is good
